	<h1 class="title">如果有些新闻素材跟电影一样，如何把它们拍成真的电影？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/99238/small/99238.jpg?1435570983" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">孙今泾 温欣语</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-23 18:19:59 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/12535/medium/12535.jpg?1437638666" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="12535" data-title="《如果有些新闻素材跟电影一样，如何把它们拍成真的电影？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/12535/medium/12535.jpg?1437638666" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/12535.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
		<!-- 新浪微博 -->
		<a data-ga-event="mobile:share:weibo" href="http://service.weibo.com/share/share.php" class="share iconfont icon-weibo" ></a>
